image_analysis.description: An interior photograph of a narrow pantry or storage area leading into a kitchen. On the left, there are white upper and lower cabinets. Several large blue water cooler jugs are stored on the counter. The floor has a black and white checkered tile pattern. Through a doorway in the background, a commercial-style kitchen is visible with stainless steel appliances, a range hood, and chairs.
